description:
Swipe right and join us for Seattle's first Tinder Party 

You've seen them online... now you can meet them in person. 

Set Tinder to 1mile, grab a drinks,  meet some matches and others that work in tech and dance to top 40, hip hop and all your favorite jams from the '00s.  Music by 92.5's DJ Kutt

...and if you're shy, we got you covered with some liquid courage.  You're guaranteed to meet someone so show up and bring your game face.

$3 cover or fill out this 3 question nightlife survey and get added to the guest list http://buff.ly/1aGhyuc
name: Tinder Swipe Right Party
